reviewText: If it's classic 2006 or so soft erotica with good quality sound/cameras and DVD quality playback you're looking for, this series is of 10 normal for the genre length DVDs. Not at all hardcore, but liberal couple fare, with a few rare and special titles in the pack that are now only available in this bundle. Some star near-celebrity actresses as seen in the Celebrity Movie Archive. At $6 to $7 each, a bargain.
